Title: Ex-File
Plot: Lt. Colonel Mann joins Gibbs in an investigation of the murder of a Marine Captain who had access to highly classified information. Things get very personal for Gibbs when one of the witnesses in the case turns out to be one of his ex-wifes.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Kathleen York, John Mallory Asher, Lilli Birdsell, Myk Watford, Robin Dunne, Susanna Thompson
